Navigate through the surface of a hypersphere and kill your enemies.
 
* Necessary packages (used in Debian 6 and Ubuntu 11.04):
  build-essential
  automake (This and below only if you do not have "configure" script generated)
  autoconf
  libtool
  libgl1-mesa-dev
  libglu1-mesa-dev
  libglew1.5-dev
  libsdl1.2-dev
  libboost-thread-dev >= 1.42
  libboost-system-dev >= 1.42
  libguichan-0.8.1-1
  libguichan-opengl-0.8.1-1
  libguichan-sdl-0.8.1-1
  libguichan-dev

-> Debian and Ubuntu users:
sudo apt-get install build-essential automake autoconf libtool libgl1-mesa-dev libglu1-mesa-dev libglew1.5-dev libsdl1.2-dev libboost-thread-dev libboost-system-dev libguichan-0.8.1-1 libguichan-opengl-0.8.1-1 libguichan-sdl-0.8.1-1 libguichan-dev

* Optional packages:
  Doxygen

* Generate configuration files:
  $ ./autogen.sh

* Compile:
  $ ./configure
  $ make -j

* Generate documentation:
  $ make doxygen-doc

* Play:
  $ cd src/sdl
  $ ./glome
